Kelly Mahon Tullier



Mr. Kelly M. Tullier is Secretary, Executive VP & General Counsel at Visa, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at The International Institute for Conflict Prevention & Resolut and Tahirih Justice Center.
Mr. Tullier was previously employed as Senior Vice President & Deputy General Counsel by PepsiCo, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Louisiana State University and a graduate degree from Cornell Law School.



